	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vir clarissime, spero me brevi venturum ad te; nunc non licuit, pergo enim recta <placeName ref="l496" cert="high">Stutgardiam</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Misi ad te literas, quę fuissent dandę d. <persName type="auto_name">Francisco Betto</persName>, nunc addo, si ille abest, dandas esse domino <persName type="auto_name">Guarnero de Castiano</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. <persName type="auto_name">Viclamus de Schartres</persName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallus</placeName>, vir magnus, omnibus numeris, quem vehementer amo, fuit nuper <placeName ref="l512" cert="high">Tubingae</placeName>; ibi nostra amicitia fuit incohata.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Habes tu quidem plurimos, qui te ament<note type="margin">a.R.: urspr. "amant" korr. "emant"!</note> et colant, sed qui te magis amet et pluris faciat, puto esse neminem.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quare debes vicissim amare.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale et salve, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullingheri</persName> optime; saluta mihi familiam, scholam atque ecclesiam; sic enim tecum soleo.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pater celestis augeat omnibus nobis sua dona, spiritum et fidem per Christum dominum nostrum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l441" cert="high">Schaffusiae</placeName> die 15. ianuarii 1564.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p3375" cert="high">Vergerius</persName> frater.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro domino <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Henrico Bullinghero</persName>, antistiti Tigurino, fratri ho[no]rando.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note>[Brief von anderer Hand, nur Unterschrift autograph.]</note>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
